msgstr "[[!img contribute/how/user_experience/interviews/gabriela.jpg link=\"no\" alt=\"Joieria artesanal afrobrasilera que amaga un llapis USB de Tails\"]]\n"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"In August, we traveled to Brazil to learn how to improve Tails for the many "
"people fighting for social change there. We trained 34 people on Tails: "
"activists, journalists, feminists, and human rights defenders."
msgstr ""
"A l'agost, vam viatjar al Brasil per aprendre a millorar Tails per a moltes "
"persones que hi lluiten pel canvi social. Vam formar 34 persones sobre "
"Tails: activistes, periodistes, feministes i defensores dels drets humans."

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"We also met Gabriela, a feminist hacker who has been training low-income "
"women from the Bahia region on using Tails."
msgstr ""
"També vam conèixer la Gabriela, una hacker feminista que ha estat formant "
"dones de baixos ingressos de la regió de Bahia sobre l'ús de Tails."

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"Gabriela introduced these women to Tails by mixing up local culture and "
"privacy technology and presenting Tails as a *patuá*, a type of Brazilian "
"protection amulet that hides the USB stick in jewelry."
msgstr ""
"Gabriela va presentar Tails a aquestes dones barrejant la cultura local i la "
"tecnologia de privadesa i presentant Tails com una *patuá*, un tipus "
"d'amulet de protecció brasiler que amaga el llapis USB a les joies."

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"These women didn't have computers of their own and used the computers at "
"work or in university or the computers of their husbands and boyfriends. "
"Tails is useful for them to work on reproductive rights but also to protect "
"their personal data from intrusive boyfriends."
msgstr ""
"Aquestes dones no tenien ordinadors propis i feien servir els ordinadors a "
"la feina, a la universitat o els ordinadors dels seus marits i parelles. "
"Tails els és útil per treballar en els drets reproductius, però també per "
"protegir les seves dades personals de les seves parelles intrusives."

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"Women working on reproductive rights understand very easily the importance "
"of privacy tools like Tails because a single mistake can compromise an "
"entire organization and get them in trouble with the police."
msgstr ""
"Les dones que treballen en drets reproductius entenen molt fàcilment la "
"importància de les eines de privadesa com Tails perquè un sol error pot "
"comprometre tota una organització i posar-los en problemes amb la policia."

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"Some of them had their home raided by the police after being denounced for "
"their work on abortion. All the information about their patients was not in "
"their phones, but in their Tails amulet, and the police couldn't find any "
"evidence about their work."
msgstr ""
"Algunes d'elles van tenir una redada polical a casa després de ser "
"denunciades pel seu treball sobre l'avortament. Tota la informació sobre els "
"seus pacients no era als seus telèfons, sinó a l'amulet de Tails, i la "
"policia no va poder trobar cap prova sobre la seva feina."

